                        <interp inst="t18730609-name-107" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY HARRIS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a cigar maker, of 9, Calvin Street, Mile End—I saw the prisoner and four men attacking Rubenstein—I saw the prisouer kick him and strike him a blow in the eye—one of the prisoner's friends hit the prosecutor across his back with a stick and he fell.</p>
